commentTextItems.html: tossed, outside off, too wide for the batsman's reach, drags his backfoot as he plays at that, Chakabva collects and whips the bails off. Zimbabwe have won the series

commentPostTextItems.html: Zimbabwe takes this by 131 runs, and they are 3-0 up with a match to go. Jarvis and Mpofu struck some early blows leaving UAE reeling at 15 for 3 in the 6th over.

Rizwan and Anwar provided some early resistance with an 82 ball 46 4th wicket stand. Then Rizwan starred again with Usman for the 5th wicket stand of 65 off 107, with Usman top scoring with 49. Burl was peak of the bowlers with 4 for 32 in his 6.2 overs
That will be all form Harare Sports Club. See you on Tuesday for the 4th ODI.  Cheers all
